OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPlans to force mobile firms
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto set out price rises     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Phone, TV and broadband customers must 
OL,6, be told about any price rises included 
OL,7, in their contract upfront and "in      
OL,8, pounds and pence" under new plans.     
OL,10,FTelecoms regulator Ofcom said it was   
OL,11,Fconcerned contracts were not providing 
OL,12,F"sufficient certainty" to customers due
OL,13,Fto many firms including mid-contract   
OL,14,Fprice hikes linked to inflation.       
OL,16,FThe move comes following a review by   
OL,17,Fthe regulator in February.             
OL,19,FMillions of customers have been hit by 
OL,20,Fbill increases due to high inflation.  
